      "comment": "WARM HUGS (3) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, finishing in the money last time when 3rd at this track over 550m. Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. One of the leading chances. WHITE MACK (8) flew the lids with a sensational early split hitting the frame with a 0.8 lengths second (30.74) over 550m at this track. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Can feature again. LEGS ELEVEN (7) has been a little hard to follow, finishing out of the placings latest but was in winning form two back scoring in a Grade 5 at Q Straight. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Has the ability and expected to do much better. BEAST ROYALE (2) is worth another chance despite missing the top-three here most recently.",
